  "texts": [
    "Table 5 indicates that the proposed approach improved outcomes compared with training the detector network with SR from other SR approaches.",
    "Figure 5 shows the precision-recall curves of the proposed approach, with and without end-to-end training, in comparison to stand-alone Faster-RCNN using LR training/ testing images.",
    "Precision and recall were determined using IoU = 0.5.",
    "One can observe that the proposed framework has superior values in precision and recall than standalone R-CNN models.",
    "End-to-end training improved the proposed method performance."
  ]
}